snippet.title: Swordash - Action Gameplay (Android/IOS)
snippet.description:
Swordash - Action Gameplay (Android/IOS)

Crazy enemies have invaded our home! The mysterious girl reappears! You are the only hero who can resist them.

-- FEATURES --
• Strategically select random skills to help you better defeat tons of enemy.
• Collect ULT disks to unlock a variety of ultimate powers.
• A wide variety of weapons and equipment with unique features to collect.
• A large number of unique bosses are waiting for you to challenge.
• Explore interesting scientific research to make you more powerful.

==========================
►► Total Size: 235MB
 
► Online/Offline: Online

► Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fattoy.swordash.android&hl=en
